thread.title: Insect farmers offer food for thought

title: Insect farmers offer food for thought
text:
Insect farmers offer food for thought 1:57pm GMT - 01:37 
Farmers in Uganda are being encouraged to use insects as livestock feed to enable them to find more nutritious protein alternatives for their animals. As Ivor Bennett reports, breeding insects like maggots and earthworms also takes up less space.
